channel.title: Alright I know I just saw a topic like this....but I need a tester
channel.description:
Yes, I know your thinking "Just test it yourself you moron" or "Stop advertising". Well I have done it myself, and it worked. But mopar server status page says its offline and I needed someone to see if its only working because its on my computer, or if others can play. Just a test would be helpful. Look here-
adminpj.no-ip.org
When this is resolved, Ill edit the text and take it off of there. Thanks.
_________________________________________________________
BTW, this server has usually been running, but after those tornadoes in arkansas hit around my house, it hasnt let connections.
